# Cycle of Kings

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and [docs/agents/](../../docs/agents/) for architecture, codegen, and game rules.

- OpenAPI first: `lib/api-spec/openapi.yaml` → `pnpm codegen`
- Schema: `lib/db/src/schema/` → `pnpm db:push`
- Building prereqs: `lib/building-progression` + enforce in `slots.ts`
- Kingdom UI: `KingdomMap.tsx` (not legacy `TownGrid.tsx`)
- Peaceful mode is permanent; peaceful towns excluded from leaderboard
